file_content.text: Those Hutts are ruthless. The things I hear they do to the Evocii....
All true. Still, have you ever actually met an Evocii?
Most pathetic things I've ever seen. Honestly, how could the Hutts not enslave a species like that?
Go meet one, then you can talk. Fifty credits says you wind up shoving it into a gutter. And laughing.
